claims:
What is claimed is:
1. A sintered high-friction cermet material consisting essentially of
boron nitride, 2 to 10 wt.%;
copper, 6 to 15 wt.%;
graphite, 3 to 11 wt.%;
boron oxide, 4 to 10 wt.%;
silicon carbide, 4 to 10 wt.%; and
iron, the balance.
